D.q[2737] = "Take the word of an old Pandawa who has sailed the seven seas of this World... Here, you\'ll spend a lot of Kamas on fermented juice and weapons. And you\'ll waste the rest talking about weapons and fermented juice... It reminds me of the time when I was a Pandawushuka disciple.... what? I haven\'t told you? One day, I came face to face with five Pandawa rebels. They were up to something, I just knew it... Fortunately, I had a Pandarium Tremens with me! Anyway, I drew my flask, we made peace, and suddenly we were as friendly as a bunch of old Lousy Pigs... Since then, I always carry one with me, it can be very useful on the rare occasion that you want to make peace. This other time... blablablablabla...";
D.q[2740] = "Hello Disciple #1! It\'s Saturday. Time for you to show me what you\'ve been learning!\nDon\'t forget to wear your outfit...";
D.q[2762] = "Let\'s say you have a friend who\'s a Fire Pandawa - get it? Well you want to buy him a present for his birthday and you know that all he wants is to destroy everything in his path. Which cloak will you get him?";
D.q[2765] = "Perfect! You\'ve mastered the basics of Pandawushu. Now the serious stuff can start. From now on, I\'ll give you a personal training session every day! You\'ll train to reach the superior levels: the Danwas...";
D.q[2772] = "You feel ready to pass the level Yondawa? Perfect! If so, you won\'t have any difficulty defeating a fighter of this level. Beat one and come back the following week to do it again. Two victories will prove your value.";
D.q[2807] = "What are you doing here? This is my place, my room... my kittie basket. If you\'re not a friend of mine, get out of here. Unless you\'re me. ARE YOU ME?! NO!!! Get out of here. Flee before it emerges and kills you!";
D.q[2826] = "So, you betray your own to get on in the world, huh?";
D.q[2853] = "To get out of here, you can either pay 64,000 Kamas of bail or wait one hour and ten minutes. \nThis jail is way too small for us to lodge such wretched beings as you all the time...";
D.q[2854] = "To get out of here, you can either pay 32,000 Kamas of bail or wait one hour.\nThis jail is way too small for us to lodge such wretched beings as you all the time...";
D.q[2855] = "To get out of here, you can either pay 16,000 Kamas of bail or wait 50 minutes. \nThis jail is way too small for us to lodge such wretched beings as you all the time...";
D.q[2856] = "To get out of here, you can either pay 8,000 Kamas of bail or wait 40 minutes. \nThis jail is way too small for us to lodge such wretched beings as you all the time...";
D.q[2857] = "To get out of here, you can either pay 4,000 Kamas of bail or wait 30 minutes. \nThis jail is way too small for us to lodge such wretched beings as you all the time...";
